g that the\neigenvalues of corresponding polynomial eigenfunctions can be determined\nalgebraically. Interestingly, the ODE of the above Rabi models are shown to be\ncharacterized, at least for some parameter range, by the same unique set of\ngrading parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Dec 2017 19:02:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 14 Apr 2018 09:29:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-20"}
