rees exactly\nwith the fluid gravity stress tensor to first order in derivatives, but\ndeviates from the later at second order and finite D.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Dec 2017 20:46:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 31 Jul 2018 09:05:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-17"}
