 as the\ndesign pattern \"MVVM\". Both datasets with Xamarin-related Q&A can be used by\nthe research community for understanding the main concerns about developing\ncross-platform mobile applications using Xamarin. In this paper, we used it for\nreplicating a studying about topic discovering.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Dec 2017 12:49:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Jul 2018 13:27:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-10"}
